description: Lists one or more Amazon Q Business conversations.

parameters.name: applicationId
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon Q Business application.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If the response is truncated, Amazon Q Business returns this token, which you can use in a later request to list the next set of messages.

nested_items.name: conversations
nested_items.description: An array of summary information on the configuration of one or more Amazon Q Business web experiences.

nested_items.name: conversationId
nested_items.description: The identifier of the Amazon Q Business conversation.

nested_items.name: startTime
nested_items.description: The start time of the conversation.
